<! DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head> 
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"> 
	<title> Gallery </title>
	<link rel="icon" href="/img/logo.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>

<body>
	<h1>{{title}}</h1> 
	
	<form id="form_login">
		<input id="input_login_email" placeholder="email">
		<input type="password" id="input_login_pass" placeholder="password">
		<button>Sign in</button>
	</form>
	
	<h3>About the Gallery</h3>
	<p>This site is great. Trust me.</p>
		<img class="landscape" src="/img/a.jpg"></img>

	<p>The goal of this website is to give people the opportunity to share their 
		interests and help them find people with similar passions.</p>
			<p>You can display your favorite books movies etc. so that other users see what intrests you</p>
		<img class="landscape" src="/img/b.png"></img>
	
	<p>You can browse galleries of other people. Leave them a like or a comment and start a new friendship!</p>
		<img class="landscape" src="/img/c.png"></img>

	<p>A very, very sophisticated search engine help you find galleries of peoples with similar tastes to give you the opportunity to find
someone who shares your passions.</p>
		<img class="landscape" src="/img/d.png"></img>
	
	<p></p>
	<h3>Below you can create your account</h3>
	<form id="form_signup">
		<p><input id="input_name" placeholder="User name *"></p>
		<p><input id="input_email" placeholder="Email *"></p>
		<p><input type="password" id="input_pass" placeholder="Password *"></p>
		<p><input id="input_city" placeholder="City"></p>
		<p><input id="input_country" placeholder="Country"></p>
		<button>Sign up</button>
	</form>
	
	<p id="message"> </p>
	{{>footer}}
	
	<script src="/js/start.js"></script>
</body>

</html>